Steve Jobs need no introduction, as even the kids around us are very well aware of this guy. 
He was more than just the co-Founder of Apple Computer and the brain behind the reinvention of 
companies like Pixar Animation Studios. Steve Jobs has always been a creative genius who pioneered the 
transformation of the computer industry and came forward to introduce revolutionary products like iMac.

Just like most other heroes, the journey of Steve Jobs also had a fair share of hardships and downfalls. 
Steve Jobs stood up through every rise and fall, taking it as an opportunity to turn things around 
and move the industry that he created, towards a better future.

-Malkeet
-June2022
